objects.name: CheatText
objects.string:
press z for more arrows
press x for more health
press c for more coins
press v to stop the screen scrolling
press k for statistics

objects.name: NewObject
objects.string: Can you make it home through the wilderness? Watch out for archers, ghosts and goblins!

objects.name: WelcomeText
objects.string:
Welcome to this game
WASD or arrows to move
Space can also be used to jump
Mouse to aim
Hold down left click to charge shots and release to shoot them

objects.name: shopWelcomeText
objects.string: Entering the shop will set your respawn point and replenish your health and quiver
